<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-07 03:40:13 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<CATEGORY> entertainment </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Marie Osmond Has Seventh Child </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PROVO, Utah (AP) -- Singer and TV host Marie Osmond has a brand  
new fan -- her seventh child. 
</P>
<P>
	Osmond gave birth to a boy, Matthew R. Blosil, early Tuesday.  
Matthew weighed in at 8 pounds, 4 ounces and was 20 inches long, 
said Melissa Kates of the PMK public relations firm. 
</P>
<P>
	The mother and baby were doing fine and his six siblings already  
have met their new brother, Kates said. 
</P>
<P>
	Marie Osmond, who is married to Brian Blosil, will return to Los  
Angeles in August to prepare for her second season opposite her 
brother in the ``Donny and Marie'' talk show. 
</P>
