<HEADLINE> Mystics 71, Liberty 63 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- Nikki McCray scored 16 points, and Chamique  
Holdsclaw added 14 as the Washington Mystics rallied in the second 
half to defeat the New York Liberty, 71-63. 
</P>
<P>
	McCray helped spark a 10-point Washington run early in the  
second half, and Holdsclaw scored 10 of the team's final 23 points 
as the Mystics held on for their second victory of the season over 
New York. 
</P>
<P>
