the tempo. Liberty point guard Teresa Weatherspoon scored a 
team-high 16 points, but New York had trouble executing its 
half-court offense throughout the second half. 
</P>
<P>
	The Liberty made just 11 of 33 field goals in the second half,  
missing several shots from in close. 
</P>
