to Soto. 
</P>
<P>
	``I think they want an immediate rematch, but that's contrary to  
the rules of the organizations,'' Arum said. ``That is something 
that has got to be sorted out.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Tyson's promoters haven't completed details for his next fight.  
  	   	
</P>
